\begin_layout Example
上述形状因子投影公式有以下奇点：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
4M^{2}\xi^{2}+\Delta^{2}\left(1-\xi^{2}\right)=0\Rightarrow\Delta^{2}=\frac{-4M^{2}\xi^{2}}{1-\xi^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

然而，参数化给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta^{2}=\frac{-4\xi^{2}M^{2}}{1-\xi^{2}}+\frac{-\sbf\Delta_{T}^{2}}{1-\xi^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf\Delta_{T}=0$
\end_inset

时
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{2}$
\end_inset

绝对值最小 ，
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta^{2}=-4\xi^{2}M^{2}/\left(1-\xi^{2}\right)$
\end_inset

，正好是奇点值。即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
-\Delta^{2}\ge\frac{4\xi^{2}M^{2}}{1-\xi^{2}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

